@round2_results
go-to: holt_wins if holt_plurality == 1; petrov_wins if petrov_plurality == 1; rovich_wins if rovich_plurality == 1; bauer_wins if bauer_plurality == 1


@holt_wins
on-arrival: president = "Holt"

As expected, the incumbent Holt wins the presidency. Let's hope he continues to keep the Nazis out of power.

@petrov_wins
on-arrival: president = "Petrov"; cp_relation = 80;

Ivan Petrov of the NCWPP has won the presidency. Immediately, the far-right launches a coup attempt against the government. We have no choice but to unite with the NCWPP against the fascists...

- @civil_war: This is civil war.

@bauer_wins
on-arrival: president = nsnawp_candidate; chancellor = "Bauer"; chancellor_party = "NSNCWP"

[? if nsnawp_candidate == "Bauer" : Rudolf Bauer of the NSNCWP has won the presidency. He wastes no time in consolidating power. ?]
[? if nsnawp_candidate != "Bauer" : The NSNCWP candidate [+ president +] has won. The first action President [+ president +] takes is inviting Bauer back into Germany, and appointing him chancellor. The Nazis waste no time in consolidating power. ?]

- @bauer_takes_power: What do we do now?


@rovich_wins
on-arrival: president = "Rovich"; reformist_dissent -= 15; Federalists_dissent -= 15; labor_dissent -= 15; left_dissent -= 5; workers_ip += 8*(1-dissent); old_middle_ip += 5*(1-dissent); new_middle_ip += 5*(1-dissent); rural_ip += 5*(1-dissent); unemployed_ip += 5*(1-dissent);

Otto Rovich of the ip has won the presidency! This is a moment of celebration for our party, and his victory is able to bolster our support.
